00:43:15.833 --> 00:43:17.166
<i>Safe in Red Hook.</i>

769
00:43:17.167 --> 00:43:18.292
The night crew?

770
00:43:18.625 --> 00:43:20.250
<i>Still onboard the</i> Northern Star.

771
00:43:26.042 --> 00:43:27.042
Good.

772
00:43:27.292 --> 00:43:28.500
We can use that.

773
00:43:31.833 --> 00:43:33.083
You know what to do.

774
00:43:33.792 --> 00:43:34.958
<i>Yes. sir.</i>

775
00:43:53.458 --> 00:43:56.541
{\an8}- [men shouting]
- [men speaking Russian]

776
00:43:56.542 --> 00:43:57.749
[explosions]

777
00:43:57.750 --> 00:43:59.417
[Karen panting]

778
00:44:03.792 --> 00:44:07.292
[men shouting. screaming]

779
00:44:24.583 --> 00:44:25.625
Oh. my God.

780
00:44:28.042 --> 00:44:29.042
He killed them.

781
00:44:30.375 --> 00:44:31.500
He killed them all.
